# musicplayergui
Welcome to nonsense module
# How do I use?
Just execute
```py
import musicplayergui as m
m.launch()
```
Or on command line
```bash
musicplayergui
```
or
```bash
python -m musicplayergui
```
# What I just update?
You don't need to click unpause now. Pause and resume are intergrated to pause button.
